147
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:18,640
- Here, take this.
- Sure.

148
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:21,120
Xia Xia! Stack them properly. The road back is bumpy.

149
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:22,720
Okay.

150
00:13:27,380 --> 00:13:28,380
Is there space for two more bags?

151
00:13:28,380 --> 00:13:29,700
Yes.

152
00:13:29,700 --> 00:13:31,720
We can leave them in the back seat, too.

153
00:13:40,500 --> 00:13:43,600
Check one more time. See if you left anything behind.

154
00:13:44,540 --> 00:13:47,080
Nope, this is everything.

155
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:48,800
I'll get these delivered in the afternoon.

156
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:50,000
Don't worry.

157
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:53,080
I'll send you anything you forgot to take back.

158
00:13:54,140 --> 00:13:56,260
I don't want to part with you guys!

159
00:13:56,260 --> 00:13:59,040
We'll stay in touch.

160
