253
00:20:29,660 --> 00:20:32,400
<i>Take Chairman Xie's car later!</i>

254
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:34,540
<i>Xia Xia! Stack them properly.</i>

255
00:20:34,540 --> 00:20:36,560
<i>- The road back is bumpy.
- Okay.</i>

256
00:20:37,540 --> 00:20:38,580
<i>Here, let me carry it.</i>

257
00:20:38,580 --> 00:20:40,320
<i>Come on, Xia Xia.</i>

258
00:20:42,280 --> 00:20:44,260
So what?

259
00:20:44,260 --> 00:20:45,840
What‘s with that answer?

260
00:20:45,840 --> 00:20:47,660
A chance and a catalyst have appeared.

261
00:20:47,660 --> 00:20:49,660
